{"tid":1363353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［錯重點］727 元朗遊行主題唔係反黑反警黑","createTime":"2019-07-25T06:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T04:47:03.000Z","uid":5627,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"41fb0166af5b6521a1d9e6130f71282308b7529c","tid":1363353,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"點解有咁多po講反黑/反警黑/請建制去<br />\n已經冇左<span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求</span>呢件事<br />\n<br />\n元朗事件其實邊個先係背後指使？<br />\n何妖？黑警？黑社會自發？<br />\n針對傀儡係冇用架<br />\n<br />\n成件事重點係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">言論自由、遊行集會自由被打壓</span> </span><br />\n我地揀元朗黎行係要講<br />\n我地唔會怕<br />\n面對暴力打壓都冇辦法滅聲<br />\n我地要攞返僅有既自由<br />\n<br />\n出去係要<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">聲援被捕義士</span></span>同爭取<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">真普選</span></span><br />\n唔可以俾焦點變得模糊<br />\n目標要一致呀各位手足<br />\n<br />\n香港加油<br />\n727見"},{"pid":"26e4ee5a10398dae6c58de4aa2f41cb942bbb74b","tid":1363353,"uid":53655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:56:00.000Z","msg":"y not all?"},{"pid":"592ea1cdcfdff2faf9169c4591b965dd886c3483","tid":1363353,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"26e4ee5a10398dae6c58de4aa2f41cb942bbb74b","tid":1363353,"uid":53655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:56:00.000Z","msg":"y not all?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:58:30.000Z","msg":"元朗遊行已經冇人講五大訴求<br />\n一定要加返落去"},{"pid":"8e78cc025c4b4d0be4c0153dc890d2e0b2854cb6","tid":1363353,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:04:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44faa2695025343dbe4c8d228cec43a4a2304733","tid":1363353,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"唔係反警黑<br />\n邊個指使黑社會做 <br />\n但又有能力令黑警合作呀"},{"pid":"62eb3f88ae9aab7ed6f4f62626a636645161165e","tid":1363353,"uid":265949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":